Hello everyone,
Here is the translation:  I'm posting this because since July 1st I've had a bad trip on LSD,
I have to say that before this bad trip I was hitting 20 joints a day and I was doing about 1 week's worth every two months with heavy use of Taz, cocaine, LSD, and all the rest... For 3 years,
Now I'm gonna tell you how it went.
A good week, waiting for you.
We had planned to take 10 grams of speed, 1 gram of MDMA, and 2 vials of LSD with 3 colleagues.
Friday evening everyone is fine
We've consumed 5 grams of speed all day.
Saturday morning after a sleepless night I'm just working in the morning from 9am to 12pm in the afternoon.
we're not continuing,
I kept on my side to tap cartridges and to tap speed,
End of the afternoon, the evening arrives 2 other colleagues join us and we had decided to take LSD on the beach (Personally I wasn't reassured),
A colleague offered me a glass with a drop from the LSD vial.
I hesitated at first then I told myself go ahead I'll take it (something I shouldn't have).
The evening is going on normally and the two so-called colleagues had decided to screw us over the colleagues.....
On this famous beach there was a lot of people and one of the two colleagues said there's no one looking for the sea, we're going to get beat....
I'm telling myself the product needs to come down because I won't be able to fight like that
so I had to resist the product,
The paranoia is starting to consume me, making a scene everywhere
The two other colleagues who hadn't taken anything, started looking for the guys who were mad at us
I'm totally wasted and he tells me he's gonna leave at some point.
